{"tid":1357424,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"看看這條撚屌如何放自己在道德高地","createTime":"2019-07-23T17:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T03:38:29.000Z","uid":21562,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4b290f534aa74082ea7fd7fa60cc6957cb1ddf36","tid":1357424,"uid":21562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:11:06.000Z","msg":"你都係唔明白雙重標準係一個有立場既人上係一定存在，寫左咁大段咁流於表面既廢話塑造自己係中立。你都係唔明白呢一切既暴力係源於背後政府多年黎拉攏商界，鄉界，係推行政策前做左幾多陰質野，拖加左幾多無形暴力係香港市民身上，淨係收唔番棕土黎起屋呢個問題都有排講，政府利益輸送養肥左幾多黑社會人士，然後令到佢地「以保衛家園」為名，以暴易暴教訓黑衣人為實，係唔講情面。所有呢排發生既事情都係反映緊政府既暴政，官員既無能，係無必要逐一譴責，逐一譴責咪好似你咁寫左成日都係冇內容既文章，你將焦點擺左自已個道德係幾咁崇高，但你忘記左呢一切發生既事都係黎自政府作為中共傀儡，多年黎一手做成既深層次矛盾。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nDjnH07.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnDjnH07.png&h=fec279e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SX9bBk8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSX9bBk8.png&h=b3a915dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YfxpbUu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYfxpbUu.png&h=da6b67e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YTtDgma.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYTtDgma.png&h=abc6dcc5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AU71d7R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAU71d7R.png&h=ec3a98de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"273134bf45bba6ca8a4e4d095b8c1c28cc82dda1","tid":1357424,"uid":264717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:13:28.000Z","msg":"打咁撚多字就世界和平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b3b55b7f8c248056f6ed09c70eacb41ad5cd5f","tid":1357424,"uid":28485,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4b290f534aa74082ea7fd7fa60cc6957cb1ddf36","tid":1357424,"uid":21562,"like":0,"d